          "text": "AI visibility tracking tools measure whether and how often your brand, products, or content appear in AI-generated answers. Specifically, they submit a library of target prompts to AI platforms such as ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, and Copilot, then record citation frequency, brand mention rate, which URLs are cited, how your brand is described, and how competitor presence compares for the same queries. The output is a statistical picture of your AI answer presence rather than a rank position."
